## Review Patterns

### Authorization Check Review

**Backend:**
```
{{patterns.auth.backend_chain}}
```

Verify every endpoint has the complete middleware chain.

**Frontend:**
```
{{patterns.auth.frontend_check}}
```

Verify UI elements are conditionally rendered based on permissions.

{{#if patterns.isolation.enabled}}
### Data Isolation Review

All database queries must include `{{patterns.isolation.field}}` filter:

```
// ✅ GOOD: Includes isolation filter
SELECT * FROM resource WHERE id = $1 AND {{patterns.isolation.field}} = $2;

// ❌ BAD: Missing isolation filter
SELECT * FROM resource WHERE id = $1;
```
{{/if}}

